'desc': [u'

Pigeon Nipple Wipes (50 Pieces) Price: Rs.995

It is always advisable to wipe the nipple clean after breastfeeding to ensure there are milk remnants around the areola. Milk remnants can cause the collection of infection-causing bacteria around the nipples that can cause problems for both mother and child. Pigeon presents the 50 piece Nipple Wipes that give you a safe
column13:
simple and hygienic way to keep nipple clean and healthy.

These soft nipple wipes are made from cotton and are soft of the sensitive skin around the nipple. These nipple wipes can also be used to wipe your baby’s hands to keep them clean after breastfeeding. These clinically tested wipes from Pigeon are packed in independent aluminium foil and ensure better hygiene for you and your baby.
